  "detailed_description": "Waves of Rotting Flesh is a stylized single player wave defense FPS. Defend a barricaded house against the hordes of the unliving, improve your abilities and weapons during the downtime between the enemy hordes, and try to survive until you can make a getaway. <br><br>The game features a selection of different weapons and enemies, various perks you can pick to improve your abilities, a regular play-mode and an endless mode. If you just want to kill some zombies for a few minutes, then this is the game for you.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1336430/extras/fea53d6bf21f73531f320d5cc397c8f6.gif?t=1594248522\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1336430/extras/fea53d6bf21f73531f320d5cc397c8f6.poster.avif?t=1594248522\" class=\"bb_img\" /></picture></span>",
  "about_the_game": "Waves of Rotting Flesh is a stylized single player wave defense FPS. Defend a barricaded house against the hordes of the unliving, improve your abilities and weapons during the downtime between the enemy hordes, and try to survive until you can make a getaway. <br><br>The game features a selection of different weapons and enemies, various perks you can pick to improve your abilities, a regular play-mode and an endless mode. If you just want to kill some zombies for a few minutes, then this is the game for you.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1336430/extras/fea53d6bf21f73531f320d5cc397c8f6.gif?t=1594248522\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1336430/extras/fea53d6bf21f73531f320d5cc397c8f6.poster.avif?t=1594248522\" class=\"bb_img\" /></picture></span>",
